OL,3,CMan dies after alleged poisoning on
OL,4,CLeicester high street
OL,6,FA man has died after an alleged
OL,7,Fpoisoning on high street.
OL,9,FLeicestershire Police said shortly
OL,10,Fbefore 1.45pm on Saturday (April 11),
OL,11,Fa report was received that a man had
OL,12,Fbeen taken unwell at an address in the
OL,13,FClarendon Park area.
OL,15,FThe incident saw a major response from
OL,16,Femergency services. Queen's Road was
OL,17,Fclosed with Leicestershire Fire and
OL,18,FRescue Service and East Midlands
OL,19,FAmbulance Service in attendance.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/3
