OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776269466
OL,3,CMan dies after alleged poisoning on
OL,4,CLeicester high street
OL,6,FOfficers said the man was treated by
OL,7,Fparamedics at the scene and taken to
OL,8,Fhospital, but died a short time later.
OL,10,FFollowing initial enquiries by
OL,11,Fofficers, a 41-year-old man was
OL,12,Farrested on suspicion of administering
OL,13,Fpoison. He has since been released on
OL,14,Fbail.
OL,16,FThe police said their investigation
OL,17,Finto the circumstances of the incident
OL,18,Fis continuing.
